OL,3,CParents fines for school absence 'need
OL,4,Cto be consigned to past'
OL,6,FMs Longfield, Executive Chair of the
OL,7,FCentre for Young Lives, said: "The
OL,8,Freasons why children miss school are
OL,9,Foften complex and there is no silver
OL,10,Fbullet.
OL,12,F"However, the one-size-fits-all and
OL,13,Foften punitive approach that previous
OL,14,FGovernments have taken to tackle
OL,15,Fabsence needs to be consigned to the
OL,16,Fpast.
OL,18,F"Simply, threatening parents with
OL,19,Ffines is not working for many families
OL,20,Fand not reducing severe absence rates."
OL,26,@oD@_OU
