OL,3,CParents fines for school absence 'need
OL,4,Cto be consigned to past'
OL,6,FSchool absence fines have increased
OL,7,Ffrom #60 to #80 under recent
OL,8,FGovernment changes to boost attendance
OL,9,Fsince the Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,11,FA parent who receives a second fine
OL,12,Ffor the same child within a three-year
OL,13,Fperiod will automatically receive a
OL,14,F#160 fine, while other actions
OL,15,Fincluding prosecution will be
OL,16,Fconsidered if a parent exceeds two
OL,17,Ffines per child in that period -
OL,18,Fleading to potential fines of up to
OL,19,F#2,500.
