OL,3,CParents fines for school absence 'need
OL,4,Cto be consigned to past'
OL,6,FThe report calls on the government to
OL,7,Ffocus its school absence strategy on
OL,8,Fearlier identification and
OL,9,Fintervention with children most at
OL,10,Frisk of absence.
OL,12,FIt suggested that rates of
OL,13,Funauthorised absence were 34% higher
OL,14,Fin the North of England than in the
OL,15,FSouth.
OL,17,FMs Longfield said: "The crucial
OL,18,Fmessage this report puts forward is
OL,19,Fthe need to intervene early and to
OL,20,Fbuild a sense of belonging and
OL,21,Finclusion in schools.
OL,26,@yD@TOU
