OL,3,CParents fines for school absence 'need
OL,4,Cto be consigned to past'
OL,6,F"Investing early in supporting
OL,7,Fchildren at risk of disengagement from
OL,8,Feducation is the best way of
OL,9,Fpreventing problems further down the
OL,10,Fline and no child should ever think
OL,11,Fthat school isn't for them."
OL,13,FCamilla Kingdon, former president of
OL,14,Fthe Royal College of Paediatrics and
OL,15,FChild Health, said: "I find the data
OL,16,Fpresented in this report terrifying.
OL,18,F"I am struck not just by the simple
OL,19,Fenormity of how many children are not
OL,20,Fin school, but the clear evidence of
OL,21,Fhow unfair this is.
OL,26,@wD@UOU
