OL,6,F"Why should a child who lives in the
OL,7,FNorth of England be at significantly
OL,8,Fhigher risk of disengaging with the
OL,9,Feducation system?"
OL,11,FThe paper highlights alternative
OL,12,Fprogrammes for tackling attendance
OL,13,Fissues, including a telepresence robot
OL,14,Fwhich sits in an absent child's seat
OL,15,Fin class and allows them to access a
OL,16,Flesson live at home.
OL,26,@qD@ROU
