OL,6,FThis has been trialled at schools on
OL,7,Fthe Wirral, Merseyside, and early data
OL,8,Fsuggests it helped boost attendance
OL,9,Fand increase the number of hours that
OL,10,Fpupils engaged with learning.
OL,12,FA Department for Education
OL,13,Fspokesperson said: "To break down the
OL,14,Fbarriers to opportunity across the
OL,15,Fcountry we must tackle the national
OL,16,Fepidemic of school absence, which
OL,17,Fremains stubbornly high after years of
OL,18,Fsoaring rates of persistent absence.
OL,26,@uD@TOU
