OL,6,F"Successfully treating the root causes
OL,7,Fof absence requires schools and local
OL,8,Fpartners to work collaboratively in
OL,9,Fpartnership with families.
OL,11,F"To support this drive, we are
OL,12,Fintroducing free breakfast clubs in
OL,13,Fevery primary school, an attendance
OL,14,Fmentoring programme, and ensuring
OL,15,Fearlier intervention in mainstream
OL,16,Fschools for pupils with special needs."
